'''Sirsir''' is a [[Babylonia]]n and [[Mesopotamian mythology|Akkadian]] god, the patron deity of [[Sailor|mariners]] and boatmen.
This name can be found in the spell book based on the [[Simon Necronomicon]], and is presented there as one of the fifty names of [[Marduk]]. He is said to be the destroyer of [[Tiamat]], and a "most powerful lord".
